  "description": "<i>Vegas Gambler</i> is a casino game for one player which features four common casino games: Video Poker, Roulette, Black Jack and Slots. <br><br>At the start of the game you have $500 to bet with. The betting limits are $200 for Black Jack and Roulette and $5 for Video Poker and Slots. Once you have placed a bet you only need to hit play, the computer will automatically bet the same amount of money again and again, however if you play roulette you have to manually place your bet on the game board. Once you run out of money you may chose between borrowing another $500 or quit. The game features a save/load function for one game.",
